<P>
 The first "City of Angels" film festival will be held Sept. 21-24 at the 
Directors Guild of America, 7920 W. Sunset Blvd.The theme, "Los Angeles in the 
Movies: Dreams, Conflicts, and Lifestyles," will feature eight major Hollywood 
