 Irwin Zucker of Hollywood says his twin grandsons, Max and Miles, 5, were 
playing with a friend until the other child had to leave. A despondent Max went 
to Grandpa, saying he now had no one to play with. Zucker told him to play with 
his brother. 
</P>
<P>
 "I can't," Max replied. "I already used him up."  
