<HEADLINE>
<P>
DISNEY DETRACTOR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Re: Disney's America ("Uncivil War Over Disney Plan," Aug. 17): I am neither a 
stuffy egghead nor of the NIMBY group and I vigorously oppose Disney's building 
their park in that area (Haymarket, Va.). 
</P>
<P>
 Anyone can take a look at the area around Disneyland in Anaheim and say "NITA 
-- Not in That Area," about Disney's America. They should put it somewhere 
else, such as someplace where the unemployment is high. 
</P>
<P>
 Watch out for Disney, they always want the local entity to supply half the 
money to build their establishments. 
</P>
<P>
 EMMA W. WILLSEY, Huntington Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
