<DOCNO> LA082294-0101 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 072141 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
August 22, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 1; Column 4; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
