19 1/4 $1.20 16 30 Hewlett-Packard 93 5/8-71 7/8 87 7/8 $5.85 15 17 Intel Corp. 
73 1/2-56 63 1/2 $5.90 11 15 Microsoft Corp. 56 3/8-39 54 7/8 $1.88A 29 25 
