accident, according to police. Police said Lopez failed a field sobriety test 
and a sample of his blood was taken for analysis. Police said they also found 
beer in his car. 
</P>
<P>
 According to police reports, Lopez was uncooperative when police tried to 
arrest him. 
</P>
<P>
